I am proud and pleased to announce that S'More has been acquired by Tawkify, the #1 Matchmaking company in America.
 
In 2019, after 10 years in the mobile and dating space, I set out to change the way people meet and date by making the experience less superficial and more meaningful. Three years later, S'More has nearly half a million users, ranks among the top recommended dating apps in the country, and has inspired an industry to create more intentional ways to connect love seekers. In addition, we created and produced the #1 celebrity dating show, with over 10 million views and 285 episodes.
 
I could not be prouder of the accomplishments of our amazing, talented, small but mighty team. They are ALL rockstars. I've never worked with a team with so much dedication, skill, and passion. Long Nguyen David Lichy Sneha Ramachandran Regina Guinto Lilia Havinson
 
Thank you to our investors who believed in this wild vision from Day 1, and have remained dedicated and committed over the years. I am so fortunate for their encouragement, guidance, and trust. Benson Oak Ventures Goodwater Ventures Gaingels Mark Pincus Dating Group LOUD Capital Pride Fund 1Boston Harbor Angels Abraham Lichy Rafael Vivas Mark Rosner Josh Gaynor Sharon Stern Ken Harris and so many more!!
 
With over 250+ employees, and hundreds of thousands of successful matches, Tawkify has aquired S'More to power the next phase of their growth with a focus on mobile. I will be joining the Tawkify leadership team to spearhead some very exciting initiatives... stay tuned for more on that soon! On top of that, our entire S'More team is coming too! Thank you to Kellie Ammerman and Kenneth Shaw for graciously welcoming our team into the fold. I cannot wait to see how we shake up the industry together!
